data.description: This one of a kind home is located down a long private driveway and features incredible upgrades & updates throughout. This unique customized floorplan offers multiple areas allowing for comfortable living and ideal for entertaining. The foyer leads to the large living room with vaulted ceiling, custom beams & floor to ceiling stone gas fireplace. Spacious kitchen with white cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, tons of storage, recessed & pendent lighting, eating area with banquette seating & large walk-in pantry with sliding barn door. The open concept floorplan opens from the kitchen to the bright family room with tons of windows & access to the expansive deck.  Main level sitting room/library leading to the rear entry foyer/mudroom with access to rear deck. The main level also features an upgraded half bath, bedroom currently used as a closet and expansive recreation room with private full bath offering multiple possibilities. The upper level primary suite features private balcony, ample closet space, built-in drawers for additional storage and a spa-like bathroom with stand alone soaking tub, large shower & dual vanities. The lower level features two spacious secondary bedrooms and third full bath. The basement features washer/dryer as well as tons of storage. The large rear yard features an above ground pool & storage shed. Updated roof in 2020, water heater in 2016 & much more.
